<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/pEyk751J31Y-FlZuHL6t6w">国行 Nintendo Switch 正式支持腾讯视频</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376873" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img16.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img16.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img16-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img16-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>昨天，腾讯视频（体验版）正式上线 Nintendo e 商店，意味着国行用户可在 Nintendo Switch 上使用腾讯视频，并支持「掌上模式」「桌面模式」和「电视模式」三种观看模式。</p>
<p>目前，该版腾讯视频包含电视剧、电影、综艺、动漫、少儿和纪录片 6 大频道，视频内容最高支持 1080P 画面清晰度。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1049367.htm">Facebook 和 Instagram 警告美国用户总统大选仍在进行中</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376874" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/f2feb3709cd9b8e.jpeg" alt="" width="700" height="642" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/f2feb3709cd9b8e.jpeg 700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/f2feb3709cd9b8e-360x330.jpeg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></p>
<p>cnBeta 消息，Facebook 和 Instagram 均在应用中加入弹窗告示美国用户「选票正在计算中」，并引导用户访问应用内其它选举相关信息。</p>
<p>在这个通知上，两款应用还增加了时间戳，以更精确地显示通知时效性。昨天，特朗普在所有选票统计完成前过早地宣称自己已经获胜。</p>
<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-11-04/doc-iiznctkc9514991.shtml">饿了么外卖可送到大兴机场登机口</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376875" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0lMrdweU4rA.jpeg" alt="" width="1271" height="847" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0lMrdweU4rA.jpeg 1271w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0lMrdweU4rA-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0lMrdweU4rA-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0lMrdweU4rA-1024x682.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1271px) 100vw, 1271px" /></p>
<p>TechWeb 消息，北京大兴国际机场和饿了么合作，开启外送服务。</p>
<p>旅客可通过大兴机场 app 或饿了么 app，让骑手将餐配送到登机口。基于机场环境的特殊性，消费者在机场下单购买的餐食将在 30 分钟内送达登机口。</p>
<p>为了适应机场内部环境，饿了么机场的「特别配送队」研发了专属的配送箱，箱子类似行李箱。</p>
<p>目前，大兴机场外卖项目上线产品涵盖 21 家餐饮品牌，近 700 款餐品，涉及中式正餐、中式快餐、咖啡茶饮、日料轻食、烘焙甜品等餐饮品类。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-04/california-projected-to-side-with-gig-economy-on-labor-issue">加州选民投票通过「22 号提案」，网约车司机将不归为雇员</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376876" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GettyImages-1219237615.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GettyImages-1219237615.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GettyImages-1219237615-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GettyImages-1219237615-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GettyImages-1219237615-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>彭博社消息，加州选民投票通过了「22 号提案（Proposition 22）」，这意味着 Uber、Lyft 司机等其它零工经济工作人员不会被视作平台的正式雇员，而是独立合同工。</p>
<p>他们将获得部分企业福利，但并不能享受完整的正式员工福利。有统计预测，Uber 和 Lyft 一年会因此节省超过一亿美元的成本。</p>
<p>周三美股收盘，打车应用 Uber 和 Lyft 双双大幅收涨，Uber 涨 14.61%，Lyft 涨 11.28%。</p>
<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-11-04/doc-iiznezxr9900826.shtml">盒马火锅正式上线盒马和饿了么</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376877" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eda9-kcieywa3144290.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="411" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eda9-kcieywa3144290.jpg 550w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eda9-kcieywa3144290-360x269.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></p>
<p>新浪消息，盒马昨天正式在全国盒马和饿了么上线发售盒马火锅。官方宣称，盒马火锅锅底数量多达 40 多种，食材种类超 2000 个，价格约为火锅店的一半。</p>
<p>盒马 3R 事业部总经理宁强表示，相信火锅的外卖占比未来能够超过一半，而盒马火锅也将被视为今冬第一大品，盒马对火锅的投入将不设上限。</p>
<h4><a href="https://36kr.com/newsflashes/953477148883332">字节跳动员工人数将突破 10 万人</a></h4>
<p>36kr 消息，字节跳动今年在国内招聘员工总数已接近 3 万人，并计划在年底前再开放 1 万个工作岗位，届时，其员工总数将突破 10 万人。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/6115560351/Jslr6c67E?from=page_1002066115560351_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime&amp;type=comment#_rnd1604477989220">上海国际旅游度假区接待游客量恢复至去年 80%</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376878" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OCR-L-DISNEY-SHANGHAI-0512-07.jpg" alt="" width="780" height="519" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OCR-L-DISNEY-SHANGHAI-0512-07.jpg 780w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OCR-L-DISNEY-SHANGHAI-0512-07-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OCR-L-DISNEY-SHANGHAI-0512-07-768x511.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" /></p>
<p>国是直通车消息，今年上海国际旅游度假区预计接待游客 1400 万人次，恢复到去年的 80%。</p>
<p>​上海迪士尼乐园于 5 月 11 日重新开园，其复工复产的做法，也成为全球迪士尼主题乐园行业重新开放、常态化条件下运营管理的标杆。</p>
<h4><a href="https://variety.com/2020/music/news/grammy-awards-change-world-music-to-global-1234821922/">格莱美「最佳世界音乐专辑奖」更名</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376879" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grammy_awards_logo.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grammy_awards_logo.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grammy_awards_logo-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grammy_awards_logo-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grammy_awards_logo-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>《Variety》消息，（美国）国家录音艺术科学学院宣布，正式将格莱美奖中的「World Music Album（世界音乐专辑）」奖项更名为「Global Music Album（全球音乐专辑）」。</p>
<p>据悉，该改变是音乐人、民族音乐学家和语言学家共同讨论的结果，旨在剔除原本奖项名中指向的「殖民主义、民俗和 ‘非美国的’」含义，以更好地适应该奖项代表的多样性和文化趋势。</p>
<h4><a href="https://luxe.co/post/125945">耐克将总部裁员人数增至 700 人</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376880" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/153654789188719431.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="563" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/153654789188719431.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/153654789188719431-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/153654789188719431-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>华丽志消息，耐克调整了其全球总部的裁员计划，裁员人数从 7 月宣布的 500 人增加到 700 人。</p>
<p>据悉，被裁员工中包括了全球总部育儿中心的 192 名工作人员。耐克将改变育儿支持策略，并在总部以外的地区推出育儿福利，将育儿机会扩大到包括零售和分销工作人员在内的数千名员工。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E5%95%86%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%945G%E5%A5%97%E9%A4%90%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%94%B94G%23&amp;Refer=top">运营商回应 5G 套餐无法改 4G</a></h4>
<p>近期，5G 套餐成为各大运营商首推的产品，有网友反馈，在运营商的 app 上，4G 套餐办理入口消失。深报视听记者实地采访发现，想从 5G 套餐改回 4G 套餐，只能到线下营业厅申请操作。</p>
<p>网友：「升级虽是趋势，但只要 4G 还存在，就应该由消费者选择用。」「日夜推销 5G 套餐就算了，还把 4G 的速度降得那么慢就过分了。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357582" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.archdaily.cn/cn/949512/orstedhua-yuan-gong-yu-qi-fu-die-jia-li-mian-yang-tai-tegnestuen-lokal">Ørsted 花园公寓 @ 丹麦</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1375954" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-Feature_Image-1.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="893" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-Feature_Image-1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-Feature_Image-1-360x268.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-Feature_Image-1-768x572.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-Feature_Image-1-1024x762.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>Ørsted 花园公寓是个翻新项目。建筑团队 Tegnestuen LOKAL 将建筑原本面向街道的普通立面彻底改造，建造了一个新的社交空间。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1375955" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/LOKAL-1.jpg" alt="" width="955" height="1000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/LOKAL-1.jpg 955w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/LOKAL-1-360x377.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/LOKAL-1-768x804.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 955px) 100vw, 955px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 建筑原貌</p>
</div>
<p>设计团队在原本开放阳台的位置建立了一系列三角型玻璃小阳台，为每户住户都创造了半私人的休息平台。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1375957" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-11-1.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="750" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-11-1.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-11-1-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-11-1-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>与此同时，可开合活动的玻璃板不仅能减少街道嘈杂的噪音，同时也可在秋冬天保持室内温暖。</p>
➜DJI Mini 2 首发评测：小机身，藏大性能
https://www.ifanr.com/1376703?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	4067
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376800 size-full" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20201101222.jpg" alt="" width="3936" height="2214" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20201101222.jpg 3936w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20201101222-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20201101222-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20201101222-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3936px) 100vw, 3936px" /></p>
<p>去年 10 月，大疆发布了御 Mavic Mini。发布之后，产品深受大众消费者的喜爱，已经帮助许多人实现了他们的航拍梦。</p>
<p>时隔一年，大疆在 11 月 5 日带来了升级之作 DJI Mini 2（下文简称 Mini 2）。在延续了 Mini 系列「249 克」、「极致便携」等核心优势的基础上，Mini 2 的飞行性能、图传性能、相机性能、智能功能等方面有了全面提升。</p>
<p><img class="wp-image-1376801 size-full aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC031982.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC031982.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC031982-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC031982-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC031982-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>来一场说走就走的旅行，上周我们前往了地处粤东的国家历史文化名城——潮州。身为无人机「小白」的我，谈谈如何用 DJI Mini 2 打开航拍新视界。</p>
<p><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=q3200a7wtp6" width="720" height="439" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"><span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span></iframe></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ DJI Mini 2 4K 拍摄，部分画质受平台压缩</p>
</div>
<h3>硬件设计</h3>
<p>Mini 2 延续了前作御 Mavic Mini 的设计语言，折叠式的机身设计与前代基本保持一致，机身仍几乎全部使用塑料材质。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376809 size-full" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-Add-7.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-Add-7.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-Add-7-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-Add-7-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-Add-7-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376807 size-full" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-17.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-17.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-17-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-17-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-17-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376808 size-full" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-82.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-82.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-82-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-82-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-82-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>与前作一样，Mini 2 的脚架仍较短，在日常飞行中我们每次起飞的地面不一定都是平整光滑的，所以需要特别注意保护飞机的摄像头，避免磕碰。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376812 size-full" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC032312.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC032312.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC032312-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC032312-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC032312-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>在附带的配件上，Mini 2 配备了和 Mavic Air 2 同款且能通用的遥控器。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376814 size-full" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-21.jpg" alt="" width="2999" height="1687" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-21.jpg 2999w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-21-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-21-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DJI-MINI2-21-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2999px) 100vw, 2999px" /></p>
<p>这款全新设计的遥控器，采用人体工程学设计，实测下来 Mini 2 整体操控手感细腻顺滑，更加适合新手操控飞行。同时，新的夹持结构设计能够更好地适配大部分全面屏手机。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376818 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b3VeHprJnM3p4PJA__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1280" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b3VeHprJnM3p4PJA__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b3VeHprJnM3p4PJA__thumbnail-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b3VeHprJnM3p4PJA__thumbnail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b3VeHprJnM3p4PJA__thumbnail-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376819 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/sPR5bqQZ0iA3s09r__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1280" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/sPR5bqQZ0iA3s09r__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/sPR5bqQZ0iA3s09r__thumbnail-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/sPR5bqQZ0iA3s09r__thumbnail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/sPR5bqQZ0iA3s09r__thumbnail-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>虽然 Mini 2 的遥控器比前代整体外观上大了很多，但换来的是更长的续航时间，大大提高了飞行拍摄的安全性。在这几天高强度的拍摄过程中，我的遥控器没有充电，但是电量仍有剩余。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376820 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/x511WCcYT7CzKZzQ__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/x511WCcYT7CzKZzQ__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/x511WCcYT7CzKZzQ__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/x511WCcYT7CzKZzQ__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/x511WCcYT7CzKZzQ__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>套装版配备了三块电池和电池管家，电池安装方式仍采用「后置式」，值得一提的是前代的电池在 Mini 2 上依旧可以通用。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376821 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7MYyKWN3W8mkW05P__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7MYyKWN3W8mkW05P__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7MYyKWN3W8mkW05P__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7MYyKWN3W8mkW05P__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7MYyKWN3W8mkW05P__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>今年 Mini 2 配备的收纳包也进行了升级。对比前代收纳包，新款的收纳包在外出游玩时，收纳和携带更加方便快捷。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376822 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Lfg3X0q57jxXU2DH__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Lfg3X0q57jxXU2DH__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Lfg3X0q57jxXU2DH__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Lfg3X0q57jxXU2DH__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Lfg3X0q57jxXU2DH__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376823 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5qiAu6OUwETvWpaD__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5qiAu6OUwETvWpaD__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5qiAu6OUwETvWpaD__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5qiAu6OUwETvWpaD__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5qiAu6OUwETvWpaD__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376824 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/oA9D1SY48p4o2UMH__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/oA9D1SY48p4o2UMH__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/oA9D1SY48p4o2UMH__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/oA9D1SY48p4o2UMH__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/oA9D1SY48p4o2UMH__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>除了设计上的延续，Mini 2 的大小和重量也跟前作看齐。紧凑式机身的 Mini 2 ，折叠后甚至与一台 iPhone SE 2 大小相近。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1376826" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CU0K6UrkvYCTEMZG__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CU0K6UrkvYCTEMZG__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CU0K6UrkvYCTEMZG__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CU0K6UrkvYCTEMZG__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CU0K6UrkvYCTEMZG__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376825 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/UYpAg2S4D8goHC7I__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/UYpAg2S4D8goHC7I__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/UYpAg2S4D8goHC7I__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/UYpAg2S4D8goHC7I__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/UYpAg2S4D8goHC7I__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>轻于 240 克的重量（含电池），使得出行无负担成为可能。此次潮州之旅，每当拍摄结束后，我都将折叠后的 Mini 2 轻松放进口袋。轻小便携的 Mini 2 真正做到了「随时起飞」。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376827 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/883H7ujLbrSkKMPb__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1280" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/883H7ujLbrSkKMPb__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/883H7ujLbrSkKMPb__thumbnail-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/883H7ujLbrSkKMPb__thumbnail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/883H7ujLbrSkKMPb__thumbnail-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>在这里也给大家科普一个无人机飞行的小知识。首先，249 克是指符合大多数国家和地区对微型无人机的重量要求。按照民航局的规定，大于 250 克以上的飞行器是需要实名登记注册的。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376828 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/q3XEgridiuEXN7RC__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/q3XEgridiuEXN7RC__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/q3XEgridiuEXN7RC__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/q3XEgridiuEXN7RC__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/q3XEgridiuEXN7RC__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>而轻于 249 克的 Mini 2，在国内或者美国、加拿大等地无需登记注册即可起飞。但是像机场等地图上的禁飞区仍然是不可以起飞的，限高区也是同样会有 120 米等不同高度的限制。所以大家不要把禁飞区和无需<a href="https://uas.caac.gov.cn/login">实名登记注册</a>弄混了。</p>
<p>另外，进行无人机飞行时除了遵守以上要求外具体还需参考当地相关的空域法规。</p>
<h3>飞行性能</h3>
<p>虽然 Mini 2 外观上看起来和上一代区别不大，但在动力性能上，Mini 2 进行了全面的提升。首先是最大飞行时间长达 31 分钟。</p>
<p>在还没接触无人机之前，很多人说无人机续航时间很短，起飞后想好怎么拍后，飞机就没电下降了。更长的续航时间带给我最直观的感受就是，无人机新手在起飞后有更多的时间去构思怎样拍的更好，再也不用匆匆按下拍摄键，从而达到拍摄更多更优质航拍内容的目的。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376829 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/USXhTgyId5z4vB8d__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1280" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/USXhTgyId5z4vB8d__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/USXhTgyId5z4vB8d__thumbnail-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/USXhTgyId5z4vB8d__thumbnail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/USXhTgyId5z4vB8d__thumbnail-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>此外，Mini 2 的电池管家收纳电池后还可作为移动电源为你的手机进行充电。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376830 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bIYsaM2x2zuC9sL9__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1280" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bIYsaM2x2zuC9sL9__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bIYsaM2x2zuC9sL9__thumbnail-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bIYsaM2x2zuC9sL9__thumbnail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bIYsaM2x2zuC9sL9__thumbnail-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>Mini 2 相比前作，抗风级别升级到了 5 级。我们在潮州韩江边进行拍摄，虽然当时的风力较大，但是 Mini 2 仍能够保持稳定的飞行姿态。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376831" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6sHJBeZCKvmDlHeV.gif" alt="" width="1200" height="673" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6sHJBeZCKvmDlHeV.gif 528w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6sHJBeZCKvmDlHeV-360x202.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>除此之外，Mini 2 在其他动力性能上也有提升。例：最大飞行速度达到 16m/s，最大起飞海拔达 4000m，最大飞行高度达 500m 等等。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376832 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/RPuQGPJdKSBirVH0__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1280" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/RPuQGPJdKSBirVH0__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/RPuQGPJdKSBirVH0__thumbnail-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/RPuQGPJdKSBirVH0__thumbnail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/RPuQGPJdKSBirVH0__thumbnail-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<h3>图传性能</h3>
<p>去年御 Mavic Mini 大家最诟病的问题就是图传较差。今年 Mini 2 升级为中高端机型所配置的 OcuSync 2.0 图传，图传距离提升至 10 公里，支持自适应双频（2.4GHz 和 5.8GHz），图传更加稳定，抗干扰能力进一步提升。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376833 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Ss7WzvkospDNuI3r__thumbnail.png" alt="" width="1920" height="887" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Ss7WzvkospDNuI3r__thumbnail.png 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Ss7WzvkospDNuI3r__thumbnail-360x166.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Ss7WzvkospDNuI3r__thumbnail-768x355.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Ss7WzvkospDNuI3r__thumbnail-1024x473.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>在江边实测飞行中我们发现，在 OcuSync 2.0 图传的加持下，Mini 2 的整体图传有较大的改善。</p>
<h3>相机性能</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>视频拍摄支持 4K 30fps 、4 倍数码变焦</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>Mini 2 在兼顾重量、体积的情况下，相机性能也得到了不错的提升。视频拍摄最高可拍摄 4K 30 fps 的高清视频，最大码率提升至 100Mbps。</p>
<p>从实拍的视频可以看出，4K 高分辨使得画质有进一步的提升，画面也更加清晰。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376834 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/u5MHuv8nGF5Efx9i__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/u5MHuv8nGF5Efx9i__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/u5MHuv8nGF5Efx9i__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/u5MHuv8nGF5Efx9i__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/u5MHuv8nGF5Efx9i__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>同时，Mini 2 视频拍摄时最高支持 4 倍数码变焦。</p>
<p>变焦操作方法也很简单， 在录像模式下，拖动 DJI Fly 飞行界面的变焦按钮，或双指在屏幕上做放大交互，或按住遥控器 Fn 按键并调节云台波轮，都可以轻松实现变焦。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376835 size-full" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cut84J1lduhe6vVW.gif" alt="" width="1273" height="589" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cut84J1lduhe6vVW.gif 1273w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cut84J1lduhe6vVW-360x167.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cut84J1lduhe6vVW-768x355.gif 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cut84J1lduhe6vVW-1024x474.gif 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1273px) 100vw, 1273px" /></p>
<p>其中 4K 格式下，2 倍画质有损；1080P 格式下，2 倍画质无损、2 倍画质有损；2.7K 格式下，3 倍画质有损。视频变焦的加入，使得在飞行创作时有了更多新的拍摄方式选择。</p>
<p><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v3200igogcr" width="720" height="439" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"><span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span></iframe></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ DJI Mini 2 4K 拍摄 2 倍变焦，部分画质受平台压缩</p>
</div>
<ul>
<li><strong>不支持「一键延时」拍摄</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>Mini 2 与前代一样，仍不支持「一键延时」。拍摄延时视频，需要前期开启「定时」拍摄，拍摄足够多的照片后，通过后期制作软件生成延时视频。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376837 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0L22RfliK8HQJz08__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="941" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0L22RfliK8HQJz08__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0L22RfliK8HQJz08__thumbnail-360x176.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0L22RfliK8HQJz08__thumbnail-768x376.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0L22RfliK8HQJz08__thumbnail-1024x502.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376836" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/yQE2k2WifkIehC80.gif" alt="" width="1200" height="673" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/yQE2k2WifkIehC80.gif 421w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/yQE2k2WifkIehC80-360x202.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ Mini 2 延时视频</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376838" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/x8TXfFfqbHlWe2Iy.gif" alt="" width="1200" height="674" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/x8TXfFfqbHlWe2Iy.gif 789w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/x8TXfFfqbHlWe2Iy-360x202.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/x8TXfFfqbHlWe2Iy-768x431.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ Mini 2 夜景延时视频</p>
</div>
<ul>
<li><strong>照片拍摄支持 RAW 格式</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>照片拍摄方便，Mini 2 支持 RAW 格式文件。RAW 格式的加入，满足了更多无人机飞手的专业需要。RAW 格式提升的不仅是照片的画质、锐度等等方面，而且可以帮助拍摄者修正前期拍摄的一些小失误。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376839 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Yz4cTKQjdnLgz5KB__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="901" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Yz4cTKQjdnLgz5KB__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Yz4cTKQjdnLgz5KB__thumbnail-360x169.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Yz4cTKQjdnLgz5KB__thumbnail-768x360.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Yz4cTKQjdnLgz5KB__thumbnail-1024x481.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<ul>
<li class=""><span class="ql-author-27190392">照片支持 </span><span class="ql-author-27190392">AEB 拍摄 </span></li>
</ul>
<p class="ql-long-27190392"><span class="ql-author-27190392">AEB 是指自动包围曝光，Mini 2 支持 AEB 三连拍，拍摄结束后自动选取曝光较正确的照片。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376856 size-full" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/222.gif" alt="" width="882" height="407" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/222.gif 882w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/222-360x166.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/222-768x354.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 882px) 100vw, 882px" /></p>
<ul>
<li>新增「全景」拍摄、「彗星」一键短片</li>
</ul>
<p>Mini 2 拥有与中高端机型一致的一键短片模式，分别是渐远、螺旋升天、冲天、环绕、彗星。其中，「慧星」是 Mini 2 的新增模式。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376840" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/oiWb877eCP7cFunx.gif" alt="" width="1200" height="673" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/oiWb877eCP7cFunx.gif 779w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/oiWb877eCP7cFunx-360x202.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/oiWb877eCP7cFunx-768x431.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ Mini 2「渐远」一键短片</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376841" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/yJVOd4bj55Qezdy8.gif" alt="" width="1200" height="671" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ Mini 2「彗星」一键短片</p>
</div>
<p>此外，Mini 2 新增「全景」拍摄。支持球形全景、180°、广角照片拍摄。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1376842" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5nquttNmoHjkjJ9E.gif" alt="" width="1200" height="553" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5nquttNmoHjkjJ9E.gif 443w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5nquttNmoHjkjJ9E-360x166.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ Mini 2「球型全景」</p>
</div>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376843 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eseBdqZN8UwtXh9p__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="363" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eseBdqZN8UwtXh9p__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eseBdqZN8UwtXh9p__thumbnail-360x68.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eseBdqZN8UwtXh9p__thumbnail-768x145.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eseBdqZN8UwtXh9p__thumbnail-1024x194.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ Mini 2 180° 照片</p>
</div>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376844 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/EuzzmoA4m2AOckGJ__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1490" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/EuzzmoA4m2AOckGJ__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/EuzzmoA4m2AOckGJ__thumbnail-360x279.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/EuzzmoA4m2AOckGJ__thumbnail-768x596.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/EuzzmoA4m2AOckGJ__thumbnail-1024x795.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ Mini 2 广角照片</p>
</div>
<h3>智能功能</h3>
<p>大疆是我认为除苹果之外，另外一家「软硬结合」做得不错的公司。DJI Fly 的编辑器，不仅有多种个性的模板可供选择，而且提供专业高级的后期制作功能。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376845 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DhbSbmdRmTHayjOM__thumbnail.png" alt="" width="1920" height="849" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DhbSbmdRmTHayjOM__thumbnail.png 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DhbSbmdRmTHayjOM__thumbnail-360x159.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DhbSbmdRmTHayjOM__thumbnail-768x340.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DhbSbmdRmTHayjOM__thumbnail-1024x453.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376846 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/XO0FxCkYO3BG7ZFN__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="856" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/XO0FxCkYO3BG7ZFN__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/XO0FxCkYO3BG7ZFN__thumbnail-360x161.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/XO0FxCkYO3BG7ZFN__thumbnail-768x342.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/XO0FxCkYO3BG7ZFN__thumbnail-1024x457.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>这次，针对 Mini 2 新产品，DJI Fly 进行了部分功能的优化和升级。</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>照片画质智能优化</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>在 DJI Fly 中，在 App 下载图片素材时，可使用照片画质智能优化功能，照片光影细节将更加生动。也可点击单张照片预览页面右下角的「魔法棒」图标，开关自动优化功能，优化后的照片/原片会自动保存至手机系统相册。</p>
<p>傍晚时拍摄的大光比照片，在开启「画质智能优化功能」后，可以看出，照片的暗部细节被提亮了，整体画面的效果得到了提升。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376847 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/fO4AOx2svEmXqQfO.gif" alt="" width="1920" height="888" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/fO4AOx2svEmXqQfO.gif 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/fO4AOx2svEmXqQfO-360x167.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/fO4AOx2svEmXqQfO-768x355.gif 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/fO4AOx2svEmXqQfO-1024x474.gif 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>「手机快传」</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>Mini 2 新增的「手机快传」功能，目前是大疆全系无人机的独占功能。配合 DJI Fly App 使用，素材下载速度可高达 20MB/s。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376848 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6PytqElL5S8dHHVW__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="982" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6PytqElL5S8dHHVW__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6PytqElL5S8dHHVW__thumbnail-360x184.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6PytqElL5S8dHHVW__thumbnail-768x393.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6PytqElL5S8dHHVW__thumbnail-1024x524.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>我们实测素材下载的过程中，下载素材甚至一度超过 20MB/s。此次出门拍摄，我特意没有携带电脑和读卡器。</p>
<p>通过「手机快传」功能，直接就完成了素材的高速下载。「手机快传」功能的加入，极大地提高了素材读取和备份的效率。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376849 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8jFoK8el8zfXbkj9.gif" alt="" width="773" height="357" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8jFoK8el8zfXbkj9.gif 773w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8jFoK8el8zfXbkj9-360x166.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8jFoK8el8zfXbkj9-768x355.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 773px) 100vw, 773px" /></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>「截选下载」</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>此外，Mini 2 新增「截选下载」功能。拍摄完的视频也可根据自己的实际需求分段进行截取选择下载，对于素材管理更加高效。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376850 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/WMxlhWSwTNsZJ3Lv__thumbnail.png" alt="" width="1920" height="851" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/WMxlhWSwTNsZJ3Lv__thumbnail.png 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/WMxlhWSwTNsZJ3Lv__thumbnail-360x160.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/WMxlhWSwTNsZJ3Lv__thumbnail-768x340.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/WMxlhWSwTNsZJ3Lv__thumbnail-1024x454.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>总的来说，Mini 2 是一款常规升级的迭代产品，大疆积极倾听消费者声音，解决了上一代产品的诟病问题。在继承了上一代产品优异基因的同时，全面提升了飞行器的多项性能，进一步降低大众消费者使用无人机的门槛。</p>
<p>另外，4K 视频拍摄、RAW 格式文件等升级，满足更多专业级用户的需求。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376851 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7EwejWIwIkKItHT2__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1280" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7EwejWIwIkKItHT2__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7EwejWIwIkKItHT2__thumbnail-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7EwejWIwIkKItHT2__thumbnail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7EwejWIwIkKItHT2__thumbnail-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>强大的性能融入轻小的机身，配备功能更加智能的 DJI Fly 软件，Mini 2 是一台出行携带使用无负担、对入门用户更加友好，同时能满足多数人拍摄需求的小飞机。</p>
<p>如果您有想购买无人机的想法或者是无人机新手用户，DJI Mini 2 将会是不二之选。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376852 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ud6743l1lT8WSaCT__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1280" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ud6743l1lT8WSaCT__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ud6743l1lT8WSaCT__thumbnail-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ud6743l1lT8WSaCT__thumbnail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ud6743l1lT8WSaCT__thumbnail-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>从第一次世界大战的无人鱼雷轰炸机到今天，无人机技术已经有了近百年的发展历史。无人机逐渐从军事领域下放到民用市场，再到今天大众消费者可以直接购买使用。无人机已经成为一个普及度非常高的产品。</p>
<p>即便这样，很多人还是担心飞行安全、苦恼拍摄创作流程复杂等等问题。而大疆 Mini 系列产品的诞生，真正做到了飞行无负担、拍摄制作流程友好，让每一位用户通过无人机可以拥有更丰富的视角和记录方式，都能体验到无人机飞行带来的乐趣。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376853 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5YeSjYSjzhbwDaps__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1280" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5YeSjYSjzhbwDaps__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5YeSjYSjzhbwDaps__thumbnail-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5YeSjYSjzhbwDaps__thumbnail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5YeSjYSjzhbwDaps__thumbnail-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>前段时间，网络上流传一段小男孩骑车追几条田坎只为看一眼无人机的视频，引起了网友们的热烈讨论。</p>
<p>事后，大疆邀请了小男孩来到深圳总部参观无人机，帮助小男孩实现了他的无人机梦想。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1376854 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9KVcxnTKNelGbNTX__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9KVcxnTKNelGbNTX__thumbnail.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9KVcxnTKNelGbNTX__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9KVcxnTKNelGbNTX__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9KVcxnTKNelGbNTX__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
